zurich life assurance plc private company information  bloomberg july    am et insurance company overview of zurich life assurance plc snapshot people company overview zurich life assurance plc provides life and general insurance products for customers in ireland the company offers individual and employer pension plans personal savings for a house or car and kids future and investments solutions it also provides life insurance solutions including family protection such as term protection pension term protection and whole of life cover mortgage protection and business protection which include key person insurance codirector insurance corporate codirector insurance partnership insurance and group risk in addition the company offers various funds including multiasset cash and bond equity property alternatives and closed funds zuri zurich life assurance plc provides life and general insurance products for customers in ireland the company offers individual and employer pension plans personal savings for a house or car and kids future and investments solutions it also provides life insurance solutions including family protection such as term protection pension term protection and whole of life cover mortgage protection and business protection which include key person insurance codirector insurance corporate codirector insurance partnership insurance and group risk in addition the company offers various funds including multiasset cash and bond equity property alternatives and closed funds zurich life assurance plc was formerly known as eagle star life assurance company of ireland limited and changed its name to zurich life assurance plc in august  the company was founded in  and is headquartered in blackrock ireland zurich life assurance plc operates as a subsidiary of zurich insurance group ltd detailed description zurich housefrascati roadblackrock  irelandfounded in  phone     fax     wwwzurichlifeie key executives for zurich life assurance plc mr anthony brennan chief 